{"tid":1178081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小修小補扯貓尾】消息指政府再讓步接納建制派提議 稍後公布詳情","createTime":"2019-05-30T07:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T10:12:20.000Z","uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d595886f5709d16766368dbe9b837351954a58e8","tid":1178081,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂引起社會激烈爭議，政府早前決定將草案直接交上大會審議。消息指，政府再作出讓步，接納建制派提出的建議，今日稍後會公布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n建制派39名立法會議員就《逃犯條例》修訂聯署去信政府，建議將移交逃犯的門檻由監禁3年提升至監禁7年，並要由當地中央機構提出引渡要求，以內地為例即要由最高人民檢察院提出。"},{"pid":"5f09fc75b425273961c3eed33af66067305e8b16","tid":1178081,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:23:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1512054/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1512054%2F&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1Q8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=b5b87245\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1512054%2F&h=a0b120fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1512054/</a>"},{"pid":"5f21401084688a8903fe0bd3ccadfe7402d1e8cb","tid":1178081,"uid":76745,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"扯完貓尾未？"},{"pid":"87ed9ed1c6d88e80f7d9fcca173bcd8e66b76e4c","tid":1178081,"uid":95,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"講到尾係唔撚信你支那啲所謂陽光司法呀屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n刑期唔夠就屈到你夠！支那丌邊個法院審理都係咁撚黑暗嫁啦！"},{"pid":"128376223d519412ef53119767c70e93b56c1afc","tid":1178081,"uid":191926,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"咪又係<br />\n一開始開天價  <br />\n之後降價  覺得人地容易接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好老實咁講<br />\n果堆所謂讓步 根本係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.3年變7年  <br />\n咪改個罪名去告<br />\n<br />\n2.